Attribution / Origin
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

grackle is a fork of "waystt", the Wayland speech-to-text tool originally
written by Artur Roszczyk (sevos):

    waystt — https://github.com/sevos/waystt
    Copyright (C) Artur Roszczyk <artur.roszczyk@gmail.com>
    Licensed under GPL-3.0-or-later

Portions of this codebase originate from waystt and remain under
GPL-3.0-or-later. The original copyright notice and license are retained. The
complete upstream commit history is preserved in this repository's git history.

Since forking, grackle has diverged substantially from upstream, including (but
not limited to): a Unix-socket control client (grackctl), continuous and
streaming transcription, local Parakeet/Nemotron transcription backends, and a
live transcript UI (grackle-ui). These changes are Copyright (C) 2025–2026 Ravi
Nagabhyru and contributors, likewise licensed under GPL-3.0-or-later.
